# SOP 1.4.1 – Patrolling Areas

**Section 1 – Patrol Operations**

## Scope

To describe how patrolling areas are defined and operated across Life Saving Victoria services, including the relationships between active patrol coverage, response capability, neighbouring service awareness, and RWC priority zones. These definitions underpin the operational use of the patrol mapping framework in LIMSOC.

